***********************************************************************
*    ABSOLUTE REGISTER EQUATES    *
***********************************
R0       EQU   0
R1       EQU   1              PARAMETER REG
R2       EQU   2
R3       EQU   3
R4       EQU   4
R5       EQU   5
R6       EQU   6
R7       EQU   7
R8       EQU   8
R9       EQU   9
R10      EQU   10
R11      EQU   11
R12      EQU   12
R13      EQU   13             ADDR OF SAVEAREA
R14      EQU   14             RETURN REG
R15      EQU   15
**************************
*    CONDITION VALUES    *
**************************
*
*    AFTER COMPARE INSTRUCTIONS (A:B)
H        EQU   2     A HIGH
L        EQU   4     A LOW
E        EQU   8     A EQUAL B
NH       EQU   13    A NOT HIGH
NL       EQU   11    A NOT LOW
NE       EQU   7     A NOT EQUAL B
*
*    AFTER ARITHMETIC INSTRUCTIONS
O        EQU   1     OVERFLOW    (ALL ONES AFTER TM)
P        EQU   2     PLUS
M        EQU   4     MINUS    (MIXED AFTER TM)
Z        EQU   8     ZERO    (ALL ZEROES AFTER TM)
NP       EQU   13    NOT PLUS
NM       EQU   11    NOT MINUS
NZ       EQU   7     NOT ZERO
*
*    AFTER TEST UNDER MASK INSTRUCTIONS
NO       EQU   14    NOT ONES
*              O, M, & Z ALSO VALID
***********************************************************************
